. Read
{jjdhm_seed}
from target
{jjdhr_heat}
. Construct
{jjdt_coronet}:
`₢` + encoded
{jjdt_firemark}
(2 chars) +
{jjdhm_seed}
(3 chars)
. Create new
{jjdpr_pace}
with:
.. Key: constructed
{jjdt_coronet}
.. `tacks`: array with single
{jjdkr_tack}:
... {jjdkm_refined}:
current timestamp (YYMMDD-HHMM)
... {jjdkm_state}:
{jjdpe_rough}
... {jjdkm_text}:
from `docket` parameter
... {jjdkm_silks}:
from argument
... {jjdkm_commit}:
capture {jjdkm_commit}
. Insert
{jjdt_coronet}
into
{jjdhm_order}
at determined position:
.. If
{jjda_first}:
